Could you add the definition which is in draft form at https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/jriou_localization/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Sites/Canonical.lean#L253 and redefine `lightProfiniteToLightCondSet`.

Great! Could you also define a `FullyFaithful` structure for this and get `Full/Faithful` instances?
